    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I ran into this and the fix was to go to Project Settings > Modules > click on the particular module > Dependencies tab. I noticed the Module SDK was still set on 1.6, I changed it to 1.7 and it worked.</p>\n"
