    "last_activity_date" : 1419077293,
    "creation_date" : 1419077293,
    "answer_id" : 27580089,
    "question_id" : 12900373,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I resolved it by setting the field blank:</p>\n\n<p>Settings > Compiler > Java Compiler > Project bytecode version</p>\n\n<p>Than IntelliJ uses the JDK default version.</p>\n"
  }, {
