    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I've hit this after just minor upgrade from IntelliJ IDEA 14 to v14.1.\nFor me changing an edit of top/parent pom helped and then clicked re-import Maven (if it is not automatic).</p>\n\n<p>But it maybe just enough to Right Click on module(s)/aggregated/parent module and Maven -> Reimport.</p>\n"
