  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/12900373/idea-javac-source-release-1-7-requires-target-release-1-7",
  "title" : "IDEA: javac: source release 1.7 requires target release 1.7",
  "body" : "<p>When running a JUnit test, using IntelliJ IDEA, I get</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/C50eY.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></p>\n\n<p>How can I correct this?</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Using SDK 1.7</li>\n<li>Module language level is 1.7</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Maven build works fine. (That's why I believe this in IDEA configuration issue)</p>\n"
